<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hire2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hire,</orth> vb. (dissyll. in <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 95</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.98" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 2, 98</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.3.36" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 3, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.291" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 291</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.1.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 1, 21</bibl>). 1) to engage in temporary service for wages: <cit><quote>--d to it by your brother,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.309" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 1, 309</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>riders dearly --d,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.14" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 14</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.98" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 2, 98</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.234" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 234</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.3.36" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 3, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 4.2.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 2, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 5.7.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 7, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.4.105" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 4, 105</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.1.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 1, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.155" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 155</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.6.122" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 6, 122</bibl>.<lb />2) to procure for temporary use at a certain price: <cit><quote>to h. waftage,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 95</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>horse to h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.268" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 268</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. rom 5.1.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 1, 26</bibl>. <cit><quote>does no --d harm,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.291" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 291</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>